hing and keep it for a time, then repeat.\"  \r\n\r\n`RelativeTtl` is currently implemented as an Absolute TTL strategy simply created from an offset from `Now`, or \"get something and keep it until <some point> and then stop caching.\"\r\n\r\nI propose changing `RelativeTtl` so that it returns a new `Ttl` when asked, each offset the same amount from the time the `Ttl` is requested.","closed_by":{"login":"reisenberger","id":9608723,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk2MDg3MjM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/9608723?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger","html_url":"https://github.com/reisenberger","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/reisenberger/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/App-vNext/Polly/issues/403/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/App-vNext/Polly/issues/403/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}